DESCRIPTION:\n\n\nView the museum with new eyes as you make your way through various exhibitions with a sketchbook in hand. You don’t need to be a professional to join\, we’ll share prompts to guide you through this drawing session.\nAll you need is an open mind and:\n-Sketchbook or A4 paper\n-Pencil (wood or mechanical) and eraser\n-Gel pens or fineliners for outlining\n-Colour brush pens\, sketch pens\, or colour pencils (no wet media)\n\n\n\n
